### Phase 5: Gemini AI Smart Categorization

#### [NEW] `server/src/services/geminiService.js` вҖ” Department Categorization Prompt

The AI prompt will be engineered to:
1. Analyze the uploaded image
2. Generate a concise title and detailed description
3. **Classify into the correct government department** from the predefined list
4. Assign severity/priority level
5. Return structured JSON

Example prompt engineering:
```
Analyze this civic issue image. Classify it into EXACTLY ONE of these government departments:
- Water Department (leaks, contamination, supply)
- Roads & Infrastructure (potholes, cracks, sidewalks)
- Electricity (streetlights, wires, grid)
- Sanitation & Waste (garbage, drains, cleaning)
- Traffic & Transport (signals, parking, highways)
- Urban Development (construction, buildings)
- Parks & Environment (trees, parks, pollution)
- General Administration (other)

Return JSON: { title, description, department, priority }
```

